Class PortChargeSubscriptionPurchases

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.geodrop.GeodropRequest
      • com.geodrop.DropPay.PortChargeSubscriptionPurchases

  • public class PortChargeSubscriptionPurchases
extends GeodropRequest
    Request used to charge customer with the previously defined price if port type is SUBSCRIPTION
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    A-Tono s.r.l.
